<p> </p>
<p>[Abonnent:Vorname | Standard:Abonnent],</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Sie haben sich vor kurzem unserer Liste angeschlossen und wir heißen Sie herzlich willkommen!</p>','<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Hi, new subscriber!</strong></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>[subscriber:firstname | default:Subscriber],</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You recently joined our list and we\'d like to give you a warm welcome!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Want to get to know us better? Check out some of our most popular articles: </p>
