<li><a href="https://www.mailpoet.com/blog/write-advice-motivation/">Just Sit Down and Write &ndash; Advice on Motivation from Ernest Hemingway</a></li>
</ol>','<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Let\'s Get Started! </strong></h1>
